  "format": "Sean, Amanda, and superfan Shea Serrano rank all 10 Fast & Furious movies (the nine mainline films plus Hobbs & Shaw), then review F9. Family, magnets, a low-stakes space walk, and nobody walks away from the ranking happy.",
  "segments": [
