      "films": [
        {
          "title": "F9",
          "year": 2021,
          "note": "Justin Lin back for the magnets, the NASCAR-car flip of Dom's father's death, and Han's return (Sung Kang, out of Lin's Better Luck Tomorrow). Sean didn't like it; the space walk plays too low-stakes; John Cena's heel turn never lands before he joins the family."
        }
